Players: Visit https://bsmnt.fun/ to explore and play games instantly. Create an account using email, wallet, or social login at https://docs.b3.fun/.[](https://docs.b3.fun/learn/getting-started/how-to-create-an-account)
Developers: Access the B3 SDK and documentation at https://docs.b3.fun/ to start building onchain games.

Stakers: Stake $B3 at https://stake.b3.fun/ to earn rewards and participate in prize games.

Hardware Enthusiasts: Preorder the B3PC at https://shop.b3.fun/ for a crypto-ready gaming experience.

